lead_paragraph: Marcus Stroman's final pitch might have been his best, a fastball that overpowered Astros star Jose Altuve to end the third inning of Houston's 7-1 split-squad win over the Toronto Blue Jays on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Rasmus, Singleton HR, Astros Split Squad Beats Blue Jays
